translation.Name: Easter Note - Crustation #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: Things have been rather rough recently. The Infection has reached Chile, cutting us off from the rest of the world. We won’t be seeing any food imports for a while… Interestingly the crabs off the shore of our lovely island seem a bit off, they are starting to turn a bit green, some even ooze puss. Something terrible is happening underwater.
